    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"sometimes the hardest thing to do is to just stop\"... what do you mean by that? like, do you mean it's okay if i just... give up? it feels like everything is just heavy and dark and there's no light at the end of it. it would be so much easier to just go to sleep and not have to deal with any of this tomorrow.",
